{"tid":470683,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"突發，教大仔又搞事！","createTime":"2017-11-16T13:55:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T15:04:46.000Z","uid":57022,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"665d0166123204ace969da3b813e883c80d16d59","tid":470683,"uid":57022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T13:55:58.000Z","msg":"有無人收到email<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/215459_384acbc94876d45fa5088cbac21325f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F215459_384acbc94876d45fa5088cbac21325f7.jpg&h=26a465f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「教大人，公民抗命！」行動宣言</strong><br />\n<br />\n明天及後天將會是教大畢業典禮，關注組成員將會在其中一天到場抗議。<br />\n<br />\n早前張仁良撲殺校內思想言論自由，擅自除下不符合港共傀儡政權立場的異議標語， 擅自公開隱私企圖以「網絡審判」來清算異議人士，本關注組對此深感不滿。<br />\n<br />\n另外，針對「國歌法」立法及「港獨違法」，本關注組在此呼籲所有同道者，以自己的方式反抗極權進入校園，例如在畢業典禮奏國歌時，雙手打叉、噓國歌或以自己的方式表示不滿，又或者到處張貼所謂「違法」的標語。我們要告訴權貴，我們不屈服於中共政權，我們要堅守下一代的思想自由，誓不成為「校園直播李飛洗腦」的幫凶。<br />\n<br />\n我們需要更多人進行集體的公民抗命，以自己的方式捍衛「教大人」以至「香港人」的尊嚴，我們要公然挑戰不合理的法律底線，行使公民不服從權！<br />\n<br />\n當港共政權告訴我們違法，我們更加要做，我們更加要告訴他們：我們不怕死，我們不怕被秋後算賬，因為我們知道所有「教大人」以至香港人將會與我們站在一起，為香港僅餘的言論自由而奮戰！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/272171616618245/photos/a.272208709947869.1073741828.272171616618245/298224730679600/?type=3&amp;notif_id=1510838821172003&amp;notif_t=like\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F272171616618245%2Fphotos%2Fa.272208709947869.1073741828.272171616618245%2F298224730679600%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26notif_id%3D1510838821172003%26notif_t%3Dlike&d=kTs28R88PNCX9IObIZg5NJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=d3c02488\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/272171616618245/photos/a.272208709947869.1073741828.272171616618245/298224730679600/?type=3&amp;notif_id=1510838821172003&amp;notif_t=like</a>"},{"pid":"908a0299e24e184a357591a09bb98bb69da40ce7","tid":470683,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T13:59:17.000Z","msg":"999"},{"pid":"ea3d598f2f49a12447c1b857d0952f8a2a067e2d","tid":470683,"uid":26303,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T14:04:43.000Z","msg":"冇人理佢，冇人關注佢，其實好快收皮"},{"pid":"511ea6c746f0b913dbe8b4e12a06cad0ac476077","tid":470683,"uid":57022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T14:23:01.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"1256231eefb2343a1c3c6924c23656951979ac9d","tid":470683,"uid":57022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T14:43:47.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"8660725886392a5c58edac626c86c661883fc44f","tid":470683,"uid":57022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T15:04:46.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}